These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, bellflower, poppy
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
4. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the person who growspoppy is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
6. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
7. the person who growssunflower is somewhere between the person who growszinnia and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
8. the person who growssunflower and the owner of the rat have the same parity positions##9
9. the person who growsbellflower and the owner of the ferret have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | zinnia | sunflower | bellflower     | poppy |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat     | guinea-pig | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, july, september, october
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in october and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
4. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | march | july | september      | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, june, november
1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
8. the person drinking cola and the person who's birthday is in march have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | cola    | fanta   | coffee    | milk  |
| Food       | march | november | october | june |

