.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
House: futuristic, colonial, townhouse, ranch-style
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. the townhouse house is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the cat and the futuristic house have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the dog and the colonial house have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
6. the colonial house is not the owner of the dog##6
7. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the futuristic house##1
9. the owner of the pony is not the ranch-style house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | futuristic | townhouse | ranch-style  | colonial |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

