3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the owner of the pony##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |  2   |     3     |      4       |
| Job   | collecting | drawing | rock-climbing | hiking |
| Pet   | goat         | pony | ferret    | chinchilla   |

