2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer and the owner of the cat have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
