2. the software-developer is on the right of the librarian##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the engineer##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the software-developer have different parity positions##9
5. the librarian is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | engineer | chef | librarian   | software-developer   |
| Hobby   | skydiving  | puzzles   | magic-tricks | gardening |

