.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, lemon, nectarine, peach
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, august, july
1. the person eating peach is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
2. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
3. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
4. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
5. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
8. the person eating garlic is the person who's birthday is in november##1
9. the person eating peach and the person who's birthday is in october have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | lemon   | peach    | nectarine | garlic    |
| Nationality   | july | october | august   | november |

