2. the fan salsa is not to the left of the tower house##8
3. the modern house is somewhere between the fan d&b and the fan salsa##7
4. the fan salsa is somewhere between the fan hip-hop and the modern house##7
5. the fan disco is not the farmhouse house##6
6. the tower house is on the right of the modern house##1
7. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
