3. the security-guard is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
4. the writer is not to the right of the freelancer##8
5. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is traveling and the electrician have the same parity positions##9
7. the person who's hobby is singing and the security-guard have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
